metadata.name: Tlaloc-Tlaltecuhtli metamorphosis
metadata.description:
Tlaloc, Mexica God of rain and lightning, is complemented by the deity Tlaltecuhtli. In this fractal metaphor they merge with each other in an infinite loop. Visual and acoustic experience that transport us to a deeply mystical and ancient plane.
Artist: Luis Torres (Lezari) in collaboration with Javier Ortiz
